PORT ELIZABETH &#8211; Andile Lungisa has resigned as ANC Regional Chairperson in Nelson Mandela Bay.Last week, the Eastern Cape Provincial Executive Committee gave Lungisa an ultimatum &#8212; step down or face disciplinary action.Lungisa, who&#8217;s also a PEC member, defied the ANC&#8217;s secretary general by standing for the position.Gwede Mantashe had warned this would violate the ANC&#8217;s constitution.